---
title: Corn Fritter Burger & Potato Fries with Slaw & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Let’s put a spin on a classic burger by replacing your standard meat patty with a flavour-packed veggie fritter, filled with
sweetcorn and melty Cheddar cheese. Stack them high between two buns with a crunchy slaw and herby mayo. Delish!
